OL,7,FMembers of the Unite union will be
OL,8,Fballoted for industrial action over
OL,9,FTata Steel's plans to close both blast
OL,10,Ffurnaces at its site, which .
OL,12,FThe union will be balloting around
OL,13,F1,500 workers at its Port Talbot and
OL,14,FLlanwern sites between 8 March and 11
OL,15,FApril. If workers vote in favour,
OL,16,FUnite says industrial action could
OL,17,Fbegin before the end of April.
